narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Magella Medical Associates Billing, Inc. is a Obstetrics & Gynecology, Maternal & Fetal Medicine provider based in Round Rock, TX. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $69.2M in Medicaid payments across 864K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $69.2M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
